--- !u!114 &600855985
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 600855984}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 630b4df3f64654b9d8f5fd62ee0318c0, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  textDisplay: {fileID: 536641343}
  sentences:
  - 'RUE: ...'
  - 'STRANGER: Finally. Took you long enough. Did you kill them for good?'
  - 'RUE: ...'
  - 'STRANGER: Your shadow. The very reason we''re both stuck here?'
  - 'RUE: *Visibly anxious* Who are...  You? And kill what?'
  - 'STRANGER: (Huh? It can''t be... This is not their first time here-...  Never
    mind.)'
  - I might kill-l-l-l my ex, not the best idea! Love that song... Just... Ignore
    it. Isn't today a lovely day?
  - 'RUE: Where... Am I?'
  - 'STRANGER: Hm?'
  - 'RUE: This... Isn''t home. *Screams* MOMM!! DADD!!!'
  - 'STRANGER: Calm down. Everyone is fine, just... Not here at the moment. But soon
    they will be (or you might).'
  - 'RUE: *Sobbing* What even is this place? Why am I here?'
  - 'STRANGER: (Oh... I guess I didn''t consider that possibility.)'
  - 'STRANGER: Let me help you, child. Allow me to introduce myself. I am the ''Keeper'',
    guardian of this world, and I can re-unite you with your family.'
  - 'RUE: How? Didn''t you say they''re not here?'
  - 'KEEPER: In this moment yes, but if you let me guide you then we can find them
    and do great things along the way.'
  - 'RUE: *Hesitantly* .. Okay. Umm, my name''s Rue and my dad''s called Rex and
    my mom Ophelia.'
  - 'KEEPER: Yeah yeah, I know. Don''t you think I''m all-knowing in this place?
    Now, allow me to explain this world to you.'
  - 'KEEPER: You are in what I call the ''Limbo'', a place where lost souls are meant
    to accept their certitude in order to pass on.'
  - 'RUE: (Accept...) Limbo?'
  - 'KEEPER: Yes. Think of it as a dream.'
  - 'RUE: Dream... Am I asleep?'
  - 'KEEPER: Yeah-.. Well, sort of. You''re not not-asleep.'
  - 'KEEPER: I need you to keep exploring. Familiarize yourself with the area I set
    up- ... Ahem, found. I have found this easier location for you to practice in.'
  - 'KEEPER: Just know the journey might be dangerous, but I will be there for you
    if something happens. Each area is referred to as a ''cycle''. Don''t be afraid
    if you don''t explore fully as cycles might repeat.'
  - 'KEEPER: Behind me are voids that I''ve NOT scattered.  These voids appear throughout
    cycles, serving as an indicator to each cycle''s exit.'
  - 'KEEPER: Use them as a guide and, most importantly, never give up. It feeds them...
    And they''re hungry.'
  - 'RUE: Them? Who''s them?'
  - 'KEEPER: My final reminder is to stay strong and to never let the voices win. '
  - 'RUE: Who''s this ''them'' you''re talking about!'
  - 'KEEPER: You are not ready to know yet.'
  - 'RUE: TELL ME!'
  - 'KEEPER: You... They are you.'
  - 'RUE: Me..?'
  - 'KEEPER: Don''t let it get to you. I promise I''ll help you. On a lighter note,
    the controls are super easy, just use the left/right ''arrow keys'' for movement
    and the ''spacebar'' to jump (Yes, it''s THAT simple.) '
  typingspeed: 0.07
  continueButton: {fileID: 1222068282}
  DialogueManager: {fileID: 1023229607}
